Package story.book.dataclient

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataClient
    DataClient is an abstract class that represents a storage location that contains Stories.
    ESClient
    ESClient is a DataClient class that represents an online storage location for Stories.
    ESCommand
    ESCommand as an abstract class that is an AsyncTask.
    ESData<T>
    ESData represents a data item stored at _index/_type/_id on our Elastic Search server.
    ESDataMatches<T>
    ESDataMatches represents a collection of data items matching a query to our Elastic Search server.
    ESRead
    ESRead is an ESCommand that reads from the Elastic Search server.
    ESResponse<T>
    ESResponse is response matching a query to our Elastic Search server, which includes header information in addition to the collection of data items.
    ESWrite
    ESWrite is an ESCommand that writes to the Elastic Search server.
    IOClient
    This class is used mainly to save stories on device, retrieve a list of stories on device, or to simply retrieve a story.
    SIDList
    Wraps an ArrayList of SIDs in order to allow serialization with JSON.
